        ],
        "dom_section_identifier": "nice-insect-bites-ng182-2020-section-0012",
        "position": 11,
        "paragraph_or_text_span": "Be aware that people may wish to consider oral antihistamines (in people aged over 1 year) to help relieve itching, even though there is uncertainty about their effectiveness in managing insect bites or stings. Some antihistamines cause sedation, which may help at night.",
