        "dom_section_identifier": "nice-insect-bites-ng182-2020-section-0020",
        "position": 19,
        "paragraph_or_text_span": "Consider referral or seeking specialist advice for people with an insect bite or sting if: they are systemically unwell they are severely immunocompromised, and have symptoms or signs of an infection they have had a previous systemic allergic reaction to the same type of bite or sting it is in the mouth or throat, or around the eyes it has been caused by an unusual or exotic insect they have fever",
