        "dom_section_identifier": "nice-insect-bites-ng182-2020-section-0022",
        "position": 21,
        "paragraph_or_text_span": "Infections of the tissues under the skin (subcutaneous), which usually result from a contaminated break in the skin. Both conditions are characterised by acute localised inflammation and oedema. The lesions are more superficial in erysipelas and have a well-defined, raised margin.",
        "normalized_span_fingerprint": "31ec31aa244f44795459907c2d3498fff25ef3e92070f278a7151ffb05749dd7",
